quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  75,20,"Alah, fiyaaku o wonah no nodditoiri…óon waasde woodeede ummital, ho…óon nganndi tag…óo mon ko adii na waawi mon wuurtinde caggal maayde, kono saabi yeddude mon ummital ko yidde mon nguurndam aduna gasajam ko yaawi."
  75,21,"Accon nguurndam laakara …óam laawol mum woni siinude yamiroore Alla, e accude ka…óaa…óe Makko karminaa…óe."
  75,22,"Geece jom en iimaan e malal e oon √±alngu na pooyni."
  75,23,"Ho…óe ndaara joom mum en wondude e dakmitaade."
  75,24,"Geece heefer…ìe hiitaa…ìe e oon √±alngu ko √±ir…ìanii…óe."
  75,25,"Na yanana nde telloto e mum lepte maw…óe muus…óe."
  75,26,"Wonah no sirku…ìe mbi*i nih wonde si …ìe maayi …ìe leptetaake, si fittaandu gooto e mum en yottiima e bororde."
  75,27,"Wi*a yogo e yim…ìe wonande wo…ì…ìe …ìe: Hombo moccata o ngam o sella."
  75,28,"O yanane oon gon…óo sukraat ndeen de woni ceertirgol makko e aduna sabu maayde."
  75,29,"Ca…óeele ndenta saanga gasirde aduna e fu…ó…óorde laakara."
  75,30,"Si …óuum laatiima maay…óo soggee faade e joom makko."
  75,31,"Oon keefeero o goon…óinaani ko nelaa…óo addi ko, o juulaani sabu Alla."
  75,32,"Kono o fennu o …óuurnii."
  75,33,"Refti o keefeero yahi to koreeji mum hombo √±aa∆¥a e yaadu mum ngam mawnakinaare."
  75,34,"Alla kammbanii keefeero o wonde lepte …ìadiimo mbo."
  75,35,"Refti O filli haala ka O daali: Hlalkaare woodanii ma e halkaare."
  75,36,"Mbela aade sikku Alla accat mbo dudoowo mbo fawaaka hay ndiga."
  75,37,"Mbela aade wonaana to…ì…ìere maniyyu yuppaande e rannga."
  75,38,"Refti o wonti caggal …óuum he…ó…óere fenndiinde, refti Alla tagi mbo, O laatini mbo tagu pooctii…óo."
  75,39,"O wa…ói e lenyol makko nooneji …ói…ói: dewel e gorel."
  75,40,"Mbela oonn tag…óo aade e tobbel maniyyu refti he…ó…óere hattanaani wuurtinde maay…ìe ngam haasbeede e yo…ìeede laawol go…óngol?Oho kay, hombo hattani."
  76,1,"Wirtiima e aade dummuna juut…óo nde o wonno baasaa…óo mbo haalatenooke."
  76,2,"Min tagrii aade to…ì…ìere jillunde ndiyam gorko e debbo, Min njariboo mbo ko Min pawi mbo ko e pawe,Min laatini mbo nanoowo ji*oowo ngam o siina ko o fawa ko e sariyaaji."
  76,3,"Min kollii mbo e …óem…óe nulaa…ìe laawol peewal, …ìanngani mbo e laawol majjere, caggal mum o wona peew…óo o sukka e laawol peewal, o wona jiyaa…óo goon…óindo jettoowo Alla, wollo o wona majjudo maggol, o wona maccu…óo keefeero jeddu…óo kaawisaaji Alla."
  76,4,"Pellet Min nkeblanii heeferbe yeddube Alla e nelaa…óo Makko callalle daasrateede faade yiite, e tonngi ko o tonngira toon, e yiite hu…ì…ìe."
  76,5,"Pellet goon…óin…ìe …óoftii…ìe na yara √±ande darnga e kaas sanngara keew…óo jillaa…óo kaafuur mbo uurangol belngol."